"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-27-How-is-Paris-allocating-budget-for-cost-effective-Summer-Games--1vzPPISzIDm-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  Paris 2024 Olympics organizers are planning major events at iconic locations like the Grand Palais and the H\\u00c3\\u00b4tel de Ville. The Paris government is demonstrating how it intends to \\\"do big things with small money\\\" \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 using existing infrastructure and minimal construction of new venues to support a world-class event while maintaining budget efficiency. Check out this breakdown about how the Paris government is allocating its budget. (This video\\u00a0is partly produced by AI.)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"